### List inquiries
GET http://localhost:4000/api/inquiries

### Inquiry detail
GET http://localhost:4000/api/inquiries/INQUIRY_ID

### Update inquiry status
POST http://localhost:4000/api/inquiries/INQUIRY_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "QUALIFIED"
}

### Update inquiry notes
POST http://localhost:4000/api/inquiries/INQUIRY_ID/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "notes": "Cliente con urgencia alta y necesidad en estrategia fiscal"
}

### List conversations
GET http://localhost:4000/api/conversations

### Conversation detail
GET http://localhost:4000/api/conversations/CONVERSATION_ID
